sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Enterprise/Admin
    participant System as Analytics System
    participant Audit as Audit Log System

    Admin->>System: Request system-level analytics
    System-->>Admin: Provide analytics data
    Admin->>System: Request message throughput metrics
    System-->>Admin: Provide throughput metrics
    Admin->>Audit: Request audit logs for compliance
    Audit-->>Admin: Provide audit logs